        "# 🌾 Crop Yield Prediction — Data Preparation\n",
        "## Objective: Prepare a feature-rich dataset for yield regression modeling\n",
        "\n",
        "**What this notebook does:**\n",
        "1. Load & clean FAOSTAT yield data (73 crops, 2000–2024, Tunisia)\n",
        "2. Classify crops into agronomic groups (each group has a different growing season)\n",
        "3. Fetch seasonal climate data from Open-Meteo for Tunisia (per year, per season window)\n",
        "4. Merge yield + climate into one unified dataset\n",
        "5. Engineer final features and save\n",
        "\n",
        "**Output:** `yield_dataset_prepared.csv` — ready for regression modeling\n"
