        "Wheat grows November–June (cool/wet season).\n",
        "Tomatoes grow March–September (warm/dry season).\n",
        "Olives grow year-round.\n",
        "\n",
        "If we join climate data without knowing the season, we'd be linking\n",
        "wheat yield to summer weather — which is wrong.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Solution:** Group crops by growing season, then fetch climate data\n",
        "for the correct seasonal window per group.\n",
        "\n",
