        "\n",
        "| Group | Season window | Example crops |\n",
        "|-------|--------------|---------------|\n",
        "| Winter cereals | Nov–Jun | Wheat, Barley, Oats |\n",
        "| Summer vegetables | Mar–Sep | Tomatoes, Peppers, Cucumbers |\n",
        "| Fruit trees | Apr–Oct | Olives, Dates, Grapes, Almonds |\n",
        "| Cool-season vegetables | Oct–Apr | Potatoes, Carrots, Onions |\n",
        "| Legumes | Mar–Jul | Chickpeas, Lentils, Peas |\n",
        "| Year-round | Full year | Sugar beet, others |"
